SEARCH
Package org.eclipse.jdt.ui.actions

Class JdtActionConstants

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.jdt.ui.actions.JdtActionConstants
public class JdtActionConstants extends Object
Action ids for standard actions, for groups in the menu bar, and for actions in context menus of JDT views.

This class may be instantiated; it is not intended to be subclassed.

Since:
2.0
Restriction:
This class is not intended to be subclassed by clients.
